| [Debian FSG compatible](/Debian_Free_Software_Guidelines) | Yes |
| [FSF](/Free_Software_Foundation) [approved](/Comparison_of_free_and_open-source_software_licences) | Yes |
| [OSI](/Open_Source_Initiative) [approved](/Comparison_of_free_and_open-source_software_licences) | No |
